p3 = momenta[0]
p4 = momenta[1]
P = sum(momenta)
Q = P[0]
pi_mag = np.sqrt(Q ** 2 / 4.0 - me ** 2)
p1 = np.array([Q / 2.0, 0.0, 0.0, pi_mag])
p2 = np.array([Q / 2.0, 0.0, 0.0, -pi_mag])
return 2.0 * qe ** 4 * (MDot(p1, p4) * MDot(p2, p3) + MDot(p1, p3) * MDot(
    p2, p4) + MDot(p1, p2) * me ** 2 + MDot(p3, p4) * mmu ** 2 + 2.0 * me **
    2 * mmu ** 2) / (MDot(p3, p4) + mmu ** 2) ** 2
